This collection includes reports, surveys, and project and training materials;
                    workshop evaluations; photocopies of newspaper articles; lists of members;
                    by-laws; administrative records related to funding and staffing; correspondence
                    with members; and National Steering Committee minutes, 1977-1981. Also included
                    are copies of the Getting It Together! newsletter, 1972-1981, and several
                    printed brochures.
